com.application.skill_level

Class AppliedSkillLevel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.application.skill_level.AppliedSkillLevel

  • @Entity
public class AppliedSkillLevel
extends java.lang.Object
    Entity that acts as a 3-way join table between Posts, Tags, and SkillLevels. Uses Post and Tag ids as a composite key. Also indicates if a particular application of tag and skill level is a bounded SkillLevel, and if so, whether it is upper or lower bounded.
    Author:
    Tim Schommer
